column2: SELECT TOP # ROW_NUMBER () OVER (ORDER BY s.specobjid DESC) AS RowNumber, s.plate, s.fiberid, s.mjd, s.ra, s.dec, s.z, s.zwarning, g.h_beta_flux, g.h_beta_flux_err, g.oiii_#_flux, g.oiii_#_flux_err, g.nii_#_flux, g.nii_#_flux_err, g.h_alpha_flux, g.h_alpha_flux_err FROM GalSpecLine AS g JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.specobjid = g.specobjid JOIN ROW_NUMBER () OVER (ORDER BY s.specobjid DESC) AS RowNum ON RowNum = RowNumber WHERE s.class = # AND s.zwarning = #
